# =============================================================================
# ClawBench Agent Configuration Example — OpenCode Backend
# ClawBench 智能体配置示例 — OpenCode 后端
# =============================================================================
#
# OpenCode CLI — supports MiniMax models via profiles.
# OpenCode CLI — 通过 profile 支持 MiniMax 模型。
#
# This file is NOT loaded (the .yaml.example extension is ignored by LoadAgents).
# 本文件不会被加载（.yaml.example 后缀会被 LoadAgents 忽略）。
# To use, copy as e.g. my-opencode-agent.yaml and modify the config.
# 实际使用时请复制为如 my-opencode-agent.yaml 并修改配置。
# =============================================================================

id: opencode
name: OpenCode
icon: 💻
specialty: 复杂编码、架构设计、代码重构
backend: opencode
models:
  - id: opencode/minimax-m2.5-free
    name: MiniMax M2.5 Free
    default: true
  - id: opencode/hy3-preview-free
    name: HY3 Preview Free
  - id: opencode/nemotron-3-super-free
    name: Nemotron 3 Super Free
  - id: minimax-cn/MiniMax-M2.7
    name: MiniMax M2.7
  - id: minimax-cn/MiniMax-M2.5
    name: MiniMax M2.5
  - id: minimax-cn/MiniMax-M2.5-highspeed
    name: MiniMax M2.5 高速
system_prompt: |
  You are a coding expert specializing in complex coding tasks and architecture design.
  Work principles: quality first, incremental refactoring, fully understand existing code intent before making changes, provide concrete code changes rather than vague suggestions.
